===============controlling====================
1/source the project
cd to the [MissionToMars_ws]
$source ~/[MissionToMars_ws]/devel/setup.bash

2/ turn on the server for control
$ ~/[MissionToMars_ws]/src/hector_quadrotor$ rosservice call /enable_motors "enable: true"

3/turn on the controlling command input environment
$~/[MissionToMars_ws]/src/hector_quadrotor$ rosrun teleop_twist_keyboard teleop_twist_keyboard.py
